EXECUTION_CONTEXT.description:
This specifies if a trade is either a combo, block, or both: e.g

EXAMPLES:

Both combo and block are present:
{
    COMBO: {
        ID: '385073621',
        COMBO_INSTRUMENT: 'BTC-CS-21SEP25-116000_119000'
    },
    BLOCK: {
        ID: 'BLOCK-225908'
    }
}

Only combo is present:
{
    COMBO: {
        ID: '385073621',
        COMBO_INSTRUMENT: 'BTC-CS-21SEP25-116000_119000'
    }
}

Only block is present:
{
    BLOCK: {
        ID: 'BLOCK-225908'
    }
}

When neither combo nor block are present, it will be an empty object: {}
